title: You can inspect components of half-completed functions!
pid: c7df1249-7c86-466e-baa7-8c79b7c8234c
body: |2-
  impossible_duplicate : (1 x : a) -> (a, a)
  impossible_duplicate x = (x, ?help)

  The REPL can now tell us that we can't use `a`.

  Main> :t help
   0 a : Type
   0 x : a
  -------------------------------------
  help : a
